    <briefdescription>
<para>Runtime PM info for device with generic PM. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Generic PM involves suspending and resuming operations which can be blocking, long lasting or asynchronous. Runtime PM API is limited when used from interrupt context. </para>
